						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up at the entrance of the Lakshmīnārāyaṇasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Achyuta, 1541 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This epigraph is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1463, Plava, Āśvija ba. 13, Monday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1541 A.D., October 17, °39.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the grant of Rājulagutti in Krottacheruvumāgāṇi by Pedirājayya under the orders of Rāmābhaṭlayya for the merit of the king.</p>						

						</summary>
